title: Week 1 Preview; Season Predictions
itunes:title: Week 1 Preview; Season Predictions
description:
Football is back! DJ & Bucky scrutinize the Le'Veon Bell drama in Pittsburgh (1:32) before they dive right into the packed week one NFL slate. The guys go game by game and preview what they will be watching on gridiron this weekend (11:15). DJ and Bucky also make their Super Bowl, MVP and rookie of the year predictions (30:16). The MTS team wraps the show by picking the biggest week two college football games (36:06).
